
        Milog 1.1 (Beta)
        - Catches SIGINT and stack overflows
        - #dump directive displays knowledge base (KB)
        - #save "filename" directive saves KB to filename
        - #load "filename" directive adds KB from filename
        - #forget directive to remove KB rules
        - #help directive for help about directives 
        - Better error messages
        - Improved lexer / parser
        - Compiles to byte-code or native executable

        Milog 1.0.1 (Beta)
        - Code cleanup
        - Added examples.pl for documentation

        Milog 1.0 (Beta)
        - Initial release
